    {
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "={{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.email }}",
        "subject": "Getting started — your first steps",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "=<h2>Ready to dive in, {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.name }}?</h2>\n<p>Now that you've had a moment to settle in, here are your first steps to get the most out of your <strong>{{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.plan }}</strong> plan:</p>\n<ol>\n  <li><strong>Explore your workspace</strong> — Check out the Google Drive folder we created for {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.company }}. It's your central hub for documents and resources.</li>\n  <li><strong>Set up your profile</strong> — Complete your account profile so your team can find and collaborate with you easily.</li>\n  <li><strong>Invite your team</strong> — Collaboration is better together! Add your colleagues so everyone can get started.</li>\n  <li><strong>Check out our guides</strong> — We have step-by-step tutorials to help you make the most of every feature.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Need a hand? Reply to this email and we'll be happy to assist.</p>\n<p>Cheers,<br>The Onboarding Team</p>",
        "options": {}
      },
