    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Client Onboarding\n\nAutomates the full welcome process for new clients.\n\nTrigger: POST /client-onboarding\nPayload: { name, email, company, plan }\n\nWhat happens:\n1. Responds 200 OK immediately\n2. Saves client data to Google Sheets\n3. Creates a Drive folder: [Company] - [Name]\n4. Sends 3 emails over 5 days:\n   - Day 0: Welcome\n   - Day 2: Getting started\n   - Day 5: Check-in\n\nCredentials: Google Sheets, Drive, and Gmail OAuth2\n\nTest it:\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:5678/webhook-test/client-onboarding \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"name\":\"Test\",\"email\":\"test@test.com\",\"company\":\"Acme\",\"plan\":\"Pro\"}'",
        "width": 440,
        "height": 520
      },
      "id": "note-node",
      "name": "Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-520, -200]
    }
